---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of use — Solana Toolbox" description="Terms of use for Solana Toolbox.">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Terms of use</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        By using Solana Toolbox you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use
        the site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">No endorsement</h2>
      <p>
        Listings on this site are community-submitted and do not constitute an endorsement,
        recommendation, or warranty of any kind. We do not audit, verify, or vouch for any listed
        tool, library, or service. Use any tool at your own risk and do your own due diligence,
        particularly for tools involving private keys, wallets, or financial transactions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        We make no guarantees that listings are accurate, complete, or up to date. The Solana
        ecosystem moves quickly — tools may be deprecated, abandoned, or changed without notice.
        If you find an inaccurate listing, please
        <a href="https://github.com/monkeybusiness-xyz/solana-toolbox/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#14F195] hover:underline">open an issue on GitHub</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Submissions</h2>
      <p>
        By submitting a tool you confirm that you have the right to do so and that the listing
        does not violate any third-party rights. We reserve the right to remove any listing at
        our discretion.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Solana Toolbox is provided "as is" without
        warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any loss or damage arising from your use of
        this site or any tool listed on it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes
        acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
